/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早起身到8點都係勁多<br />\n返工返學呀大佬 好心你地出去近少少就行下啦"},{"pid":"55ae5d383f2968c279b3b63c44a511d5d5ee59b8","tid":828721,"uid":5490,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:12:33.000Z","msg":"$2搭車限時段，返工放工時間唔比用，自然無晒d廢老"},{"pid":"d825ed722cef7855142901efc9d24a1991eaf266","tid":828721,"uid":33359,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:13:31.000Z","msg":"等緊1a 係人都知1a係最多廢老去搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廢老行得又慢 又成身老人除 搞到成個車箱都臭哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋佢地最能鐘意係返工放工時間搭車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n專能登就阻鳩住你班候生仔 從中獲得快感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日返工個陣 條隊已經排得好長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩我早出門口 都叫排到隊頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁就玩下電話等車 玩玩下眼尾睇到有個廢老直接行係隊頭隔離等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就睇下你夠唔夠打我尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等左幾分鐘架車就到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個廢老果然係想打尖 仲直接一支拐杖隊埋黎擋鳩住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我即刻氣聚丹田 大大聲&quot;喂&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嚇能到佢拐杖都跌鳩埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大大聲屌七佢 &quot;想打我尖 你傻能左啊&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟手直接上車 上車個陣仲唔小心將佢支拐杖踢入巴士車底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi